channel.title: Artim! Join our team today!
channel.description:
Who we are: We are a few dedicated and talented players/coders that enjoy the rsps community and wish to build upon it. We host 2 servers, a 718 and a 317, both of which are very well put-together with very few/no bugs, glitches, etc. We love what we do and we show it it our work.
What we need: We are currently in need of an advertiser/youtuber.
If you are interested, then please send me a message on skype ~ loli8yourcat
~Cheers
